outputs.output_descr: This project is a multi-disciplinary approach to strengthening good governance systems through  promotion of accountability and transparency, accessible to justice, promotion and protection of human rights, and strengthened Government Communications.

project_descr: The Strengthening Transparency Integrity and Rule project aims at facilitating national good governance initiatives particularly in Anti-corruption, Legal Sector Reform and Law enforcement, Vital Registration and Communications.
project_title: Strengthening  Transparency, Integrity & Rule of Law
